<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">&gt; Free-scaling UIs were tried for years before that and never once got to acceptable quality.<p>The web <i>is</i> a free-scaling UI, which scales &quot;responsively&quot; in a seamless way from feature phones with tiny pixelated displays to huge TV-sized ultra high-resolution screens.  It&#x27;s fine.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44371572&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44369646%2344371572" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
